729506f-a.title: Richmond: Richmond Terrace - Houseman Avenue
729506f-a.text:
264O Richmond Terrace, adjeining the S.W. corner ef Houseman
Avenue. Beers's map ef 1874, and Rebinson's maps of 1898 and
1907 show it te have been the Herry Miller house.
September 28, 1924.
Wm. T. Davis through P.L. Sperr
